<h1>Login</h1>
<p>You can use this form to log in to the application.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
 
<ul>
 <li><strong>User name</strong> - enter your user name.<br />
 If you want to log in to a domain other than <a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-webapp/administration/settings/activedirectory">the default domain</a>, use the form <em>domain@login</em> or <em>login@domain</em>.</li>
 <li><strong>Password</strong> - enter the password.</li>
 <li><strong>Keep me signed in</strong> - enable this option if you want to log in permanently to the application on this computer, i.e. the next time you use it on this computer you will not need to log in again.</li>
</ul>

	
</asp:Content>
